item.title: What does this mean?
item.dc:creator: @Bmaw Bmaw
item.description:
@Bmaw wrote:

Right click on your compiler > edit

Then erase all of it and replace it with

@echo off Title Compiler "C:\Program Files\Java\jdk1.6.0_13\bin\javac.exe" *.java pause

item.title: What does this mean?
item.dc:creator: @Fat_Cookies Fat Cookies
item.description:
@Fat_Cookies wrote:

Open the batch file and post it here.

Should look like:

"c:\program files\java\jdk1.5.0_06\bin\javac.exe" *.java
pause

Unless the command is correct, then you need to change jdk1.5.0_06 to jdk1.6.0_13
